  "question": "<p><span data-contrast=\"auto\">Which </span><span data-contrast=\"none\">among the following are the basic tenets of Liberalism?</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559685&quot;:360,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\"> </span></p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"%1.\" data-font=\"\" data-listid=\"23\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"1\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">Man is a Rational Creature.</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233279&quot;:true,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\"> </span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"%1.\" data-font=\"\" data-listid=\"23\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"1\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">There is no basic contradiction between an individual’s self-interest and the common interest of society.</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233279&quot;:true,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\"> </span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"%1.\" data-font=\"\" data-listid=\"23\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"1\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">It promotes civil liberties of the individual.</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233279&quot;:true,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\"> </span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"%1.\" data-font=\"\" data-listid=\"23\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"1\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">It upholds freedom of contract.</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233279&quot;:true,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\"> </span></li>\r\n</ol>",
  "option1": "1 and 2",
  "option2": "1,2 and 3",
  "option3": "1, 3 and 4",
  "option4": "1,2,3 and 4",
  "option5": "",
  "answer": "1,2,3 and 4",
  "explanation": "<p><span data-contrast=\"none\">Liberalism insists on liberty of individual and its first and foremost goal is liberation from restraints </span><span data-contrast=\"none\">particularly</span><span data-contrast=\"none\"> imposed by an </span><span data-contrast=\"none\">authoritarian</span><span data-contrast=\"none\"> state. </span><span data-contrast=\"none\">It</span><span data-contrast=\"none\"> basic tenets include</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559685&quot;:360,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\"> </span></p>\r\n<ol>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"%1.\" data-font=\"Calibri\" data-listid=\"37\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"1\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">Man is a rational </span><span data-contrast=\"none\">creature</span><span data-contrast=\"none\"> because he has an immense potential to contribute to his own good as well as the good of </span><span data-contrast=\"none\">society</span><span data-contrast=\"none\">,</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233279&quot;:true,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\"> </span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"%1.\" data-font=\"Calibri\" data-listid=\"37\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"1\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">Liberalism upheld the reconciliation of the common interests between the interest of individual and the society.</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233279&quot;:true,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\"> </span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"%1.\" data-font=\"Calibri\" data-listid=\"37\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"1\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">It promotes civil liberties which include, </span><span data-contrast=\"none\">freedom</span><span data-contrast=\"none\"> of </span><span data-contrast=\"none\">thought</span><span data-contrast=\"none\"> and expression, freedom of association, etc.</span><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233279&quot;:true,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\"> </span></li>\r\n<li data-leveltext=\"%1.\" data-font=\"Calibri\" data-listid=\"37\" aria-setsize=\"-1\" data-aria-posinset=\"1\" data-aria-level=\"1\"><span data-contrast=\"none\">It held that state will look after the legality </span><span data-contrast=\"none\">of</span><span data-contrast=\"none\"> the enforcement of contract</span><b><span data-contrast=\"none\">.</span></b><span data-ccp-props=\"{&quot;134233279&quot;:true,&quot;201341983&quot;:0,&quot;335559739&quot;:160,&quot;335559740&quot;:259}\"> </span></li>\r\n</ol>"
}